{
  "stem": "7069.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So anyways, when that time was up, nothing had happened yet either.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then after a while, it was one more time, and he says, now look, you guys, we don't want to stand here all day long, either.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So if nothing happens in the next 10 minutes, if you don't have to-- if you haven't brought your kids over here to the other side, our guards will come in and we will force you-- we will separate you forcefully.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then of course, what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The guards came in and grabbed the kids and shoved them over to the other side.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And some of them hollered, hey, wait a minute.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm, I'm 14.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm 15.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He said 13 age.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so-- and the guards didn't even pay any attention.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "These were big, tall guys.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They took their big boots and kicked the kids over to the other side.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There were these two women standing with infants on their, on their arms.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The one guard came over, grabbed the infant, jerked it out of her arm, and threw it over into the other side of the ramp among the other children that were there already, at which moment, this other woman with the infant on the arm quickly went over to drop the child there.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She stayed there for a while, then she was forced back, too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yet I have to say-- and I wonder if kids can imagine it in this respect-- the worst scene that ever-- that I ever saw was the separation of children from their, from their loved ones.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's an indescribable scene.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I don't even want to talk much more about that.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
